taxi_id.name: taxi_id
taxi_id.comment: A unique identifier for the taxi.

trip_start_timestamp.name: trip_start_timestamp
trip_start_timestamp.comment: When the trip started, rounded to the nearest 15 minutes.

trip_end_timestamp.name: trip_end_timestamp
trip_end_timestamp.comment: When the trip ended, rounded to the nearest 15 minutes.

trip_seconds.name: trip_seconds
trip_seconds.comment: Time of the trip in seconds.

trip_miles.name: trip_miles
trip_miles.comment: Distance of the trip in miles.

pickup_census_tract.name: pickup_census_tract
pickup_census_tract.comment: The Census Tract where the trip began. For privacy, this Census Tract is not shown for some trips.

dropoff_census_tract.name: dropoff_census_tract
dropoff_census_tract.comment: The Census Tract where the trip ended. For privacy, this Census Tract is not shown for some trips.

pickup_community_area.name: pickup_community_area
pickup_community_area.comment: The Community Area where the trip began.

dropoff_community_area.name: dropoff_community_area
dropoff_community_area.comment: The Community Area where the trip ended.

tips.name: tips
tips.comment: The tip for the trip. Cash tips generally will not be recorded.

trip_total.name: trip_total
trip_total.comment: Total cost of the trip, the total of the fare, tips, tolls, and extras.

payment_type.name: payment_type
payment_type.comment: Type of payment for the trip.

pickup_latitude.name: pickup_latitude
pickup_latitude.comment: The latitude of the center of the pickup census tract or the community area if the census tract has been hidden for privacy.

pickup_longitude.name: pickup_longitude
pickup_longitude.comment: The longitude of the center of the pickup census tract or the community area if the census tract has been hidden for privacy.

pickup_location.name: pickup_location
pickup_location.comment: The location of the center of the pickup census tract or the community area if the census tract has been hidden for privacy.

dropoff_latitude.name: dropoff_latitude
dropoff_latitude.comment: The latitude of the center of the dropoff census tract or the community area if the census tract has been hidden for privacy.

dropoff_longitude.name: dropoff_longitude
dropoff_longitude.comment: The longitude of the center of the dropoff census tract or the community area if the census tract has been hidden for privacy.

dropoff_location.name: dropoff_location
dropoff_location.comment: The location of the center of the dropoff census tract or the community area if the census tract has been hidden for privacy.
